title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1982-04-12
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko > Minglewood Blues, Peggy-O, Mama Tried, Mexicali Blues, Bird Song, C.C. Rider, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain, Deal

Set 2

Women Are Smarter > Sugaree, Estimated Prophet > Uncle John's Band > Drums > The Other One > Stella Blue > Sugar Magnolia

E: (I Can't Get No) Satisfaction
